Dialogue: 0,0:36:31.90,0:36:33.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一切都是为了夏洛特殿下
Dialogue: 0,0:36:33.54,0:36:41.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等……把阿莉亚还给我
Dialogue: 0,0:36:41.78,0:36:43.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你最好不要勉强
Dialogue: 0,0:36:43.82,0:36:45.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乖乖地睡在那里吧
Dialogue: 0,0:36:45.50,0:36:47.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还给我
Dialogue: 0,0:36:48.57,0:36:50.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是难缠啊
Dialogue: 0,0:36:50.28,0:36:51.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干掉她吧
Dialogue: 0,0:36:51.46,0:36:52.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:37:01.14,0:37:01.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙是……
Dialogue: 0,0:37:02.62,0:37:04.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 夏洛特殿下
